{"type":"message","id":"82263f94","parentId":"cf045e92","timestamp":"2026-05-03T17:05:44.447Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:473c6328-4063-457e-b666-f5e57d816e89 Wiki Logging - Reese] Execute: python3 ~/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-heartbeat.py reese\n\nThis logs recent conversations to the wiki at ~/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/daily-logs/. Read the wiki-heartbeat.py script and follow its logic.\nCurrent time: Sunday, May 3rd, 2026 - 1:05 PM (America/New_York) / 2026-05-03 17:05 UTC"}],"timestamp":1777827944396}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3345753","parentId":"82263f94","timestamp":"2026-05-03T17:05:53.067Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to execute a wiki heartbeat script for \"reese\". Let me first read the script to understand what it does.\n","thinkingSignature":"9b6943418a1ae73d791b8cfd63241be5b8df282da178f789799de12a8628094a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fhwk2e722zbe_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-heartbeat.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":16301,"output":67,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16496,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777827944447,"responseId":"0646b368e5354d486295ee9fab84743d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c60524d","parentId":"d3345753","timestamp":"2026-05-03T17:05:58.313Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fhwk2e722zbe_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nWiki Heartbeat Logger\nCalled every 30 minutes via cron for each agent.\nLogs recent conversations to memory-wiki daily logs.\n\"\"\"\n\nimport json\nimport sys\nimport os\nimport subprocess\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nWIKI_ROOT = Path.home() / \"agent-mission-control\" / \"memory-wiki\"\nLOGS_DIR = WIKI_ROOT / \"daily-logs\"\nSTATE_FILE = WIKI_ROOT / \".heartbeat_logger_state.json\"\n\ndef get_openclaw_sessions(agent_id):\n    \"\"\"Get recent sessions using openclaw CLI.\"\"\"\n    try:\n        result = subprocess.run(\n            [\"openclaw\", \"sessions\", \"list\", \"--agent\", agent_id, \"--json\"],\n            capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=15\n        )\n        if result.returncode == 0:\n            return json.loads(result.stdout).get(\"sessions\", [])\n    except:\n        pass\n    return []\n\ndef get_session_messages(session_key):\n    \"\"\"Get messages from a session.\"\"\"\n    try:\n        result = subprocess.run(\n            [\"openclaw\", \"sessions\", \"history\", session_key, \"--json\", \"--limit\", \"30\"],\n            capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=15\n        )\n        if result.returncode == 0:\n            return json.loads(result.stdout)\n    except:\n        pass\n    return []\n\ndef load_state():\n    \"\"\"Load last logged session info.\"\"\"\n    if STATE_FILE.exists():\n        with open(STATE_FILE) as f:\n            return json.load(f)\n    return {}\n\ndef save_state(state):\n    \"\"\"Save state.\"\"\"\n    with open(STATE_FILE, \"w\") as f:\n        json.dump(state, f)\n\ndef log_conversation(session_key, agent_id, messages):\n    \"\"\"Log a conversation to today's daily log.\"\"\"\n    today = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n    log_file = LOGS_DIR / f\"{today}.md\"\n    \n    if not log_file.exists():\n        with open(log_file, \"w\") as f:\n            f.write(f\"# {today} - Daily Log\\n\\n---\\n\\n\")\n    \n    # Extract meaningful exchanges\n    entries = []\n    current_bobby = None\n    \n    for msg in messages:\n        role = msg.get(\"role\", \"\")\n        content = msg.get(\"content\", \"\")\n        \n        if isinstance(content, list):\n            content = \" \".join(c.get(\"text\", \"\") for c in content if isinstance(c, dict))\n        \n        if not content or len(content.strip()) < 2:\n            continue\n        \n        if role == \"user\":\n            # Skip very short messages (just \"ok\", \"thanks\", etc)\n            if len(content.strip()) > 2:\n                current_bobby = content[:1000]\n        elif role == \"assistant\" and current_bobby:\n            # Skip very long responses\n            display_content = content[:800] + \"...\" if len(content) > 800 else content\n            entries.append((current_bobby, display_content))\n            current_bobby = None\n    \n    if entries:\n        with open(log_file, \"a\") as f:\n            f.write(f\"\\n### {agent_id.upper()} × Bobby\\n**Time:** {datetime.now().strftime('%H:%M')}\\n\\n\")\n            for bobby_msg, agent_msg in entries:\n                f.write(f\"**Bobby:** {bobby_msg}\\n\")\n                f.write(f\"**{agent_id.upper()}:** {agent_msg}\\n\\n\")\n\ndef main():\n    if len(sys.argv) < 2:\n        print(\"Usage: wiki-heartbeat.py <agent_id>\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n    \n    agent_id = sys.argv[1]\n    state = load_state()\n    state_key = f\"{agent_id}_last_session\"\n    \n    sessions = get_openclaw_sessions(agent_id)\n    new_logs = 0\n    \n    for session in sessions[:3]:  # Check last 3 sessions\n        session_key = session.get(\"key\", \"\")\n        if not session_key:\n            continue\n        \n        # Skip if already processed\n        if state.get(state_key) == session_key:\n            continue\n        \n        messages = get_session_messages(session_key)\n        if messages:\n            log_conversation(session_key, agent_id, messages)\n            state[state_key] = session_key\n            new_logs += 1\n    \n    save_state(state)\n    print(f\"Heartbeat: logged {new_logs} new conversation(s) for {agent_id}\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777827958313}}
{"type":"message","id":"22123571","parentId":"4c60524d","timestamp":"2026-05-03T17:06:09.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the script. It:\n1. Gets recent sessions for the agent using `openclaw sessions list --agent <agent_id> --json`\n2. For each new session, gets recent messages via `openclaw sessions history <session_key> --json --limit 30`\n3. Logs meaningful exchanges to `~/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/daily-logs/{today}.md`\n4. Uses a state file to track which sessions have already been logged\n\nLet me run the script.\n","thinkingSignature":"934cdb4b531691902aa1b8f2b8d521024e07c81f99f89fe5d8e6690a97531207"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gykjqsgdxxcq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 ~/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-heartbeat.py reese","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1037,"output":152,"cacheRead":16384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17573,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777827958314,"responseId":"0646b37c453708f8a85c4d0c6f65ae01"}}
